            _vm._v(
              "While  adjusting  the  most  important  terms  and  phrases  in  the Christian  system,  in  order  to  a  more  perspicuous  and comprehensive intelligence of it, it is expedient that we should also advert to other predicates of the genuine Christian. The five terms at the head of this chapter are all indicative of his "
